law.history: Repealed 2013 Ky. Acts ch. 49, sec. 10, effective June 25, 2013. -- Amended 2000 Ky. Acts ch. 225, sec. 4, effective July 14, 2000. -- Created 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 224, sec. 9, effective July 15, 1994.
